quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  10,34,"Boola mbu; “Alikho mu abo abamutsokasinjia Nyasaye ninabo ulia owachachia okhuloonga ebilonje, mana alibikalusia?" Boola mbu; “Nyasaye niye wachachia ebilonje khandi niye ulibikalusia. Kho mukalukhanibungwa hena?”"
  10,35,"Boola mbu; “Koo, khulikhomwo nende mubamutsokasinjia Nyasaye abo ulunjisinjia khubwatoto?” Boola mbu; “Nyasaye niye ulunjisinjia khubwatoto. Kho ulia ulunjisinjia khubwatoto shiniye ukhoyekhane muno okhuloondwa nohomba ulia ulalunjisinjia halali okhula alunjisibwe? Kho muli nende shina, mubusinjia murie?""
  10,36,"Ne abanji babu balondanga butswa amaparo kabu, ne okhuparirisia shikhukhonyakhwo imbeli wobwatoto shiosishiosi tawe. Toto Nyasaye amanyile muno koosi akabakholanga."
  10,37,"Ne shikanyalikhana mbu Ikurani ino yakasibwasa, mbu shirula khu Nyasaye tawe, halali ifuchilisania nende akali imbeli wayio, ne ni amebaalo keshitabu shibula obukanakani, ne shirula khu Nyasaye Omulesi webiloonje bioosi."
  10,38,"Nohomba baboolanga mbu yachikasia butswa omwene. Boola mbu; “Mana khetsekhwo nende Isura ndala ili shinga ino. Mana mulanje bamunyala balali Nyasaye tawe, toto nimuli abahabwene.”"
  10,39,"Halali bakatsula akababula ninako obulaamba, ne obwatoto bwako bushili okhuboolela. Ne endio nilwa bakatsula balia bali imbeli wabu. Kho lola shinga indukho yabandu ababii yali."
  10,40,"Ne mubo baliwo basuubilanga muyo, ne mubo baliwo balasuubilanga muyo tawe. Ne Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi amanyile muno abakholanga obwononi."
  10,41,"Ne nibakhukatsula, boola mbu; ‘‘Endi nende ebikhole bianje, nanyu muli nende ebikhole bienyu. Enywe muli ehale nende akekholanga, ne esie siesi endi ehale nende akamukholanga.”"
  10,42,"Ne mubo baliwo bakhuwulilisinjia. Ne koo, wakhanyala okhukhola abekala amarwi bawulila kata nibalekhonyelanga obwongo tawe?"